query:
SELECT ff.*, ef.formandoId, f.nome as formandoNome, c.nome as cenarioNome 
FROM fotos_formando ff 
JOIN execucoes_formando ef ON ff.execucaoFormandoId = ef.id 
JOIN formandos f ON ef.formandoId = f.id 
LEFT JOIN cenarios c ON ff.cenarioId = c.id 
WHERE f.nome LIKE '%Álvaro Pontual%' 
ORDER BY ff.id DESC 
LIMIT 50
